## Academic Use

This project is part of a Masters dissertation at King's College London. If you use
this code or methodology in your research, please cite:

Whitenburgh, P. (2025). ESG Rating Changes and Stock Returns: A State Policy Analysis.
Masters Dissertation, King's College London.

## Data Attribution

This project uses data from multiple sources:
- Sustainalytics ESG ratings
- CRSP/Compustat financial data  
- Fama-French factor data
- State-level environmental policy data

Please ensure proper attribution and licensing compliance when using this project
with proprietary datasets.
